- Chunk storage: `{CHUNK_STORAGE_PATH}/{video_id}/{resolution}/seg_%04d.ts` — see ADR 010
- Nginx routing rules: which URL paths proxy to which service — [FILL: define before infra setup]
- Message queue: Redis List for now; RabbitMQ upgrade planned (discussion pending)

